Mistakes can happen....

I had a '66 Deluxe that the factory letter said was originally shipped to
Hawaii. Despite the fact it was a European Tourist delivery picked up in
Norway and driven around Europe before being shipped to Canada. I had some
of the bills from the original owner to prove this......... A bit of a
difference......

